# 2026-04-20: extraction-run audit trail. Keep the small JSON summaries in git
# so the rule-state and per-column firing counts are versioned alongside the
# code, but ignore the per-paper binary snapshots (parquet) which are large
# and only needed locally for diff_extraction_runs.py.
!outputs/extraction_runs/
outputs/extraction_runs/*/binary_classifications.parquet
outputs/extraction_runs/*/literature_review_enriched.parquet
outputs/candidate_database_phase1.csv
outputs/conference_attendance_summary.csv
outputs/analytical_techniques_by_discipline.csv
outputs/conference_texts/
outputs/techniques_*.csv
outputs/abstracts_technique_counts.csv
# 2026-07-03: extraction-validation pipeline (gold labels + rule backlog) —
# small, versioned tables consumed by later validation-pipeline tasks.
!outputs/validation/
!outputs/validation/*.csv

